Maintainer: Kenton Russell <kent.russell@timelyportfolio.com>
Description: plottableR provides easy htmlwidget access in R to the powerful open-source
  Plottable.js from Palantir Technologies.  From its own description,
  "Plottable.js consists of pluggable set of Components which encapsulate
  rendering logic, and a layout engine that is responsible for positioning them."
